.PP
Convert RST grid tables to list-tables.
.IP "1." 3
Convert grid tables in a file to list-tables.
The result is output to stdout:
.RS 4
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
$ listtable.py input.rst
\f[R]
.fi
.RE
