$ listtable.py input1.rst input2.rst
$ listtable.py *.rst
\f[R]
.fi
.RE
.IP "3." 3
Use pipe (but \f[C]cat\f[R] might not keep the encoding):
.RS 4
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
$ cat in.rst | listtable.py -  | untable.py - > out.rst
\f[R]
.fi
.RE
